com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.location
Interface LocationPackage

public interface LocationPackage

The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type

See Also:
LocationFactory
